    ðŸ”¹ `foo2hp -p[...]`  --> ðŸ“„ Select paper size. Example: `foo2hp -pLetter` or `foo2hp -pA4`
    ðŸ”¹ `foo2hp -m[...]`  --> ðŸŒˆ Print mode (monochrome or color).  Example: `foo2hp -m1` for black and white.

